      "translation": "E501 Series"
    },
    {
      "key": "contribution.{57644AE6-7FFA-A501-8FE0-7567171D3CEF}.description",
      "source": "常磐線取手以遠にも投入できるように、209系をベースに交直両用、最高速度120kmとして制作された。",
      "translation": "Based on the 209 series, it was manufactured as an AC/DC dual-current train with a maximum speed of 120 km/h, so it could be introduced beyond Toride on the Joban Line."
    },
    {
